name: Jamie Mitchell
text: This location sucks.  It's been over 75 minutes for delivery  and took over 10 minutes to get anybody on the phone  to even locate my order and that person couldn't tell any info.  Not the first time either.   Thought I'd try again after a year  but the service is just as crappy.  I will contact my credit card to fight the charge.

name: Jonathan Vizcardo
text: They are closed no store in moorpark anymore been closed for 2 years now
